    "description": "寻宝之旅是一款 3D 益智冒险游戏，您需要引导一位海盗穿越充满谜题的岛屿，寻找隐藏的宝藏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/234280f6c2d4620ababb2fbac4e02df9.poster.avif?t=1721058220\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/234280f6c2d4620ababb2fbac4e02df9.webm?t=1721058220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/234280f6c2d4620ababb2fbac4e02df9.mp4?t=1721058220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>自由旋转和移动摄像机，找到最佳路径。<br></li><li>奔跑、挖掘并巧妙地利用重力来克服障碍。<br></li><li>收集钥匙以解锁装满战利品的宝箱。<br></li><li>升级您海盗的靴子和铲子，让寻宝之旅更快速、更强大！<br></li><li>探索各种令人惊叹的岛屿，每个岛屿都有独特的挑战。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/523118612119f440e31016c5ffba1257.poster.avif?t=1721058220\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/523118612119f440e31016c5ffba1257.webm?t=1721058220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/523118612119f440e31016c5ffba1257.mp4?t=1721058220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
